{"tid":412640,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"返工遲到的理由：手機升級 Android 8.0 了","createTime":"2017-09-24T23:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T04:54:39.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0094d4b72926760b878c459f64423391589947b7","tid":412640,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T23:29:17.000Z","msg":"Google 在 8 月底正式公佈 Android 8.0 的名字，以朱古力夾心餅 Oreo 命名的新系統擁有不少新功能。現時 Google 的 Nexus 和 Pixel 手機和裝置已經率先取得系統更新，而各大手機品牌亦準備為舊機推出系統更新，當然新推出的手機亦會使用 Android 8.0 Oreo。<br />\n<br />\n不過新系統似乎還有不少問題，不少 Pixel 手機在更新後出現各式各樣的問題，最近在 Reddit 討論區，有 Nexus 和 Pixel 手機用戶表示，在升級 Android 8.0 Oreo 後鬧鐘會出現自動崩潰的情況，令到預設的鬧鐘失效。結果就是令他們返工遲到，從留言的人數看來，不少用戶都由中招。<br />\n<br />\n有網民表示鬧鐘不響令自己連續遲到 3 天，有網民甚至要向老闆解釋遲到原因，又說已經準備好改用 iPhone。最慘的是，有網民表示鬧鐘偶爾出問題，當他望著手機時鬧鐘還會響，但設定第二天早上的鬧鐘，手機又不響了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/09/24/返工遲到的理由：手機升級-android-8-0-了/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F%E8%BF%94%E5%B7%A5%E9%81%B2%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%9A%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-android-8-0-%E4%BA%86%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=J%2FTFY9WdWstxb25PVIE3NsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=c2eb3d4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/09/24/返工遲到的理由：手機升級-android-8-0-了/software/android-app/</a>"},{"pid":"936e751d316cd94475e23ebcb28b5c05cb93cbf4","tid":412640,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T23:34:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>Android 8.0一個Bug玩死上班一族！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n近日有更新Android O的Pixel、Nexus用戶在Reddit論壇反映，更新Android 0之後，鬧鐘App出現自動問題，導致預設的鬧鈴失效，很多人因此上班遲到。從反饋來看，中招的人不在少數！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201709/21/nnf2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201709%2F21%2Fnnf2.png&h=31b7019a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 目前，Google尚未修復這一問題，只能用第三方鬧鐘App來代替。</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/25145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F25145&d=J%2FTFY9WdWstxb25PVIE3NsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a9ee21a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/25145</a></div>"},{"pid":"6c86d47e862763be0a3e83acbc9ba8461c055a9d","tid":412640,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T23:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>Android 8.0一個Bug玩死上班一族！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n近日有更新Android O的Pixel、Nexus用戶在Reddit論壇反映，更新Android <span style=\"color: red;\">8.0</span>之後，鬧鐘App出現自動問題，導致預設的鬧鈴失效，很多人因此上班遲到。從反饋來看，中招的人不在少數！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201709/21/nnf2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201709%2F21%2Fnnf2.png&h=31b7019a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 目前，Google尚未修復這一問題，只能用第三方鬧鐘App來代替。</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/25145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F25145&d=J%2FTFY9WdWstxb25PVIE3NsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a9ee21a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/25145</a></div></blockquote>"},{"pid":"50a8e15f33dc040d94a96cec99f10f62a4796dd6","tid":412640,"uid":121772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T23:51:23.000Z","msg":"我pixel冇事喎"},{"pid":"d506ac277a15c4bb38346cbef15d418ce6102be9","tid":412640,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T23:53:13.000Z","msg":"其實部分7plus上ios11 開頭都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但reset一次就冇事"},{"pid":"1a7742ea22555e20920eaf2c5d940cbe1477c9ca","tid":412640,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c